About the Series:
Detective Superintendent Peter Boyd is the leader of a police team which investigates 
unsolved murders using modern technology.
Starring  Trevor Eve, Sue Johnston and Wil Johnson.  

Episode 1 & 2 "Waking The Dead" (The Pilot)
Boyd decides to have a second attempt at cracking the case of Alice Miller, a young girl who 
was raped and murdered five years ago

Episode 3 & 4 "Burn Out"
When a young woman, Marina, sets alight an abandoned car in the middle of a busy street, 
and takes photographs of it as it burns

Episode 5 & 6 "Blind Beggar"
Workmen renovating the crypt of a Catholic church are alarmed when they discover the 
skeletal remains of a young man buried within the concrete.

Episode 7 & 8 "A Simple Sacrifice"
New evidence comes to light in the case of Annie Keel, a woman who was tried and 
convicted twenty-five years ago of a double murder.

Episode 9 & 10 "Every Breath You Take"
When the corpse of well-known police woman Debbie Britton, who disappeared a year 
earlier, is found floating in a golf bag in the River Thames
